# CryptoTradingBot

## Overview

CryptoTradingBot is an automated trading bot for cryptocurrency markets. This project allows users to automate their trading strategies and execute trades on supported cryptocurrency exchanges.

## Features

- **Exchange Integration**: Connect with popular cryptocurrency exchanges via API (e.g., Binance, Coinbase Pro).
- **Trading Strategies**: Implement custom trading strategies based on technical indicators, market signals, or user-defined rules.
- **Backtesting**: Test trading strategies against historical data to evaluate performance.
- **Real-time Trading**: Execute trades in real-time based on predefined conditions.
- **Portfolio Management**: Monitor and manage cryptocurrency holdings and trading activities.
- **Security**: Implement security best practices to safeguard API keys and user data.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Python (version 3.6 or higher)
- Pip (Python package installer)

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/CryptoTradingBot.git
   cd CryptoTradingBot
